additions.gui.witherstormmod.config.convertFalling: Specifies if the Wither Storm should convert falling blocks into clusters (NOTE: This can be very laggy and cause the Wither Storm to evolve fast!).
Specifies if the Wither Storm should heal whenever it eats a mob (determined by half the mob's max health).
additions.gui.witherstormmod.config.tractorBeamFlu:
Specifies the height of which tractor beams should remove water. The default of 63 is ocean height and upwards.
Range: -64 ~ 320
additions.gui.witherstormmod.config.tractorBeamsRe: Makes it so the Wither Storm will remove fluids above Y 63 with its tractor beams.
additions.item.witherstormmod.iron_command_tool.in: Deals it's damage twice, once as normal damage and then again as piercing damage!
